[panicked breathing]

17
00:00:59.225 --> 00:01:01.102
[music becomes distorted]

18
00:01:01.186 --> 00:01:04.898
[woman laughs]

19
00:01:04.981 --> 00:01:06.399
[eerie crackling]

20
00:01:06.483 --> 00:01:08.318
[laughs]

21
00:01:10.653 --> 00:01:12.030
[yelps]

22
00:01:12.113 --> 00:01:13.865
-[unsettling music playing]
-[woman chuckles]

23
00:01:14.908 --> 00:01:15.825
Oh! [laughs]

24
00:01:15.909 --> 00:01:18.787
[panicked breathing]

25
